item.title: Credits
item.description: Contributors Right now, it’s mostly been a one-man show, but all PR will be considered. Contributions are welcome! .ghContributors{ display:flex; flex-flow: wrap; align-content: flex-start } .ghContributors div{ width: 50% ; display: inline-flex; margin-bottom: 5px; } .ghContributors div label{ padding-left: 4px ; } .ghContributors div span{ font-size: x-small; padding-left: 4px ; } @machellerogden 149 commits Prior Art Without the work of many many devs before me, specifically the authors of packages such as rc, minimist and inquirer, this project might have never gotten off the ground.
